WEBVTT

01:40.479 --> 01:45.920
[Speed and Love]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.840
[Episode 16]

02:09.110 --> 02:11.290
♪ What would I do? ♪

02:11.320 --> 02:13.790
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

02:12.830 --> 02:13.560
Are you done?

02:14.350 --> 02:17.050
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

02:17.340 --> 02:17.990
How is it?

02:17.530 --> 02:19.680
♪ I don't think so ♪

02:20.750 --> 02:21.590
You look like a chef.

02:21.250 --> 02:23.520
♪ What would I do ♪

02:23.570 --> 02:25.940
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

02:26.570 --> 02:29.300
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

02:29.480 --> 02:31.940
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

02:32.760 --> 02:35.950
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

02:36.480 --> 02:39.170
♪ Find you where you are ♪

02:39.640 --> 02:41.890
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

02:42.090 --> 02:44.740
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

02:42.750 --> 02:43.540
Your tomato.

02:45.520 --> 02:48.490
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

02:48.829 --> 02:51.670
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

02:52.070 --> 02:54.370
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

02:54.400 --> 02:56.870
♪ To accompany me too ♪

03:03.380 --> 03:05.620
♪ Would you like that? ♪

03:06.290 --> 03:09.190
♪ Would you like that? ♪

03:21.660 --> 03:22.340
Is it good?

03:22.940 --> 03:25.260
♪ What would I do? ♪

03:24.470 --> 03:25.100
It's good.

03:25.280 --> 03:28.020
♪ If I could fly up on the roof ♪

03:25.470 --> 03:26.600
Have some more then.

03:28.920 --> 03:30.270
♪ Would I rob a bank? ♪

03:31.070 --> 03:33.770
♪ Oh, I don't think so ♪

03:34.340 --> 03:34.990
Alright.

03:35.270 --> 03:36.750
Time to add some ketchup.

03:37.060 --> 03:38.660
I'll get the ketchup myself.

03:40.390 --> 03:42.480
♪ Would you like that? ♪

03:42.380 --> 03:43.040
Why is it...

03:43.360 --> 03:45.480
♪ Would you like that? ♪

03:47.380 --> 03:48.190
Are you okay?

03:49.220 --> 03:50.780
It's fine. I'll go change.

03:52.500 --> 03:53.500
I'll go with you.

04:11.250 --> 04:12.010
Let me see.

04:14.360 --> 04:15.760
There's so much ketchup.

04:17.709 --> 04:19.640
Wear black. You look cool in black.

04:21.390 --> 04:22.070
Okay.

04:32.060 --> 04:33.140
You are so pale.

04:34.900 --> 04:36.500
That area never gets any sun.

04:42.909 --> 04:44.270
I didn't mean to look.

04:58.540 --> 04:59.470
Help me put it on.

05:37.830 --> 05:40.430
The two fish you caught today
are really plump.

05:40.470 --> 05:42.510
Do you think they weigh
at least 6 to 7 jin?

05:42.510 --> 05:44.470
I've never failed at fishing.

05:47.070 --> 05:48.600
Why is the kitchen light on?

05:50.159 --> 05:50.620
This...

05:50.780 --> 05:52.010
Mu, you're home?

05:52.030 --> 05:53.740
What happened to the kitchen?

05:54.340 --> 05:55.590
Mom, I want ice cream.

05:55.620 --> 05:58.020
There's some in the fridge. Help yourself.

05:59.740 --> 06:01.110
Mom, where's my tablet?

06:01.420 --> 06:02.510
Isn't it in your sister's room?

06:02.510 --> 06:03.640
Go get it from there.

06:07.980 --> 06:08.860
Wait, don't go.

06:09.480 --> 06:10.360
She's asleep.

06:15.810 --> 06:18.270
You hide inside.
I'll go out and handle this.

06:20.910 --> 06:21.910
Why should I hide?

06:21.950 --> 06:22.880
This is my house.

06:23.720 --> 06:24.780
What if they find out

06:24.780 --> 06:26.150
that we're in a room with the lights off?

06:26.150 --> 06:27.410
It wouldn't look good.

06:27.710 --> 06:29.240
Neither of us needs to hide.

06:29.380 --> 06:31.380
You're acting guilty for no reason.

06:32.150 --> 06:33.070
You're not nervous?

06:33.070 --> 06:33.830
Not at all.

06:34.420 --> 06:35.060
How...

06:35.890 --> 06:36.950
do you manage that?

06:40.680 --> 06:42.610
How am I supposed to prove it to you?

06:44.740 --> 06:46.110
Are you thinking of
something inappropriate?

06:46.110 --> 06:47.140
Who thought that way first?

06:47.140 --> 06:47.700
You did.

06:51.190 --> 06:52.720
Mom, Sister is still awake.

06:56.300 --> 06:57.070
Mu.

06:57.630 --> 06:58.890
You're not yet asleep?

06:59.340 --> 07:02.800
If you aren't, your sister will be
heading in to get her tablet.

07:03.250 --> 07:03.900
Go ahead.

07:13.180 --> 07:13.710
Brother?

07:14.070 --> 07:14.800
Your tablet.

07:17.040 --> 07:18.440
Did you receive the rice?

07:18.980 --> 07:21.070
Yes, we'll try it tonight.

07:22.530 --> 07:24.720
Zhao, stay for dinner tonight.

07:24.900 --> 07:26.560
Jin Qiang caught two big fish.

07:27.030 --> 07:28.330
Sure, let me cook a dish or two.

07:28.330 --> 07:29.330
Forget it.

07:29.830 --> 07:31.290
With your cooking skills,

07:31.430 --> 07:33.030
you are going to ruin my fish.

07:33.300 --> 07:34.220
I'll cook it myself.

07:34.220 --> 07:35.480
Then be quick about it.

07:37.270 --> 07:38.670
Jiang Mu is in for a treat.

07:42.500 --> 07:43.180
Fishing?

07:44.070 --> 07:44.860
Eating fish.

07:45.800 --> 07:47.460
Jin Qiang caught two big fish.

07:50.320 --> 07:51.130
Mu.

07:51.710 --> 07:52.510
What's wrong?

07:53.150 --> 07:54.350
Are you feeling warm?

07:54.860 --> 07:55.390
What...

07:56.100 --> 07:57.360
What's with your face?

07:57.580 --> 07:58.900
It looks a bit flushed.

08:00.180 --> 08:01.860
What were you two doing in the room?

08:01.860 --> 08:03.950
The light kept turning on and off.

08:05.150 --> 08:06.740
The switch isn't working properly.

08:06.740 --> 08:08.000
I was helping to fix it.

08:08.100 --> 08:09.980
Nothing works properly in this house.

08:09.980 --> 08:11.710
There's always one thing or another
that is broken.

08:11.710 --> 08:13.270
Don't worry. Queue up.

08:13.740 --> 08:15.250
I'll fix everything one by one.

08:15.250 --> 08:16.450
You're first in line.

08:16.590 --> 08:17.700
First, quit drinking.

08:17.700 --> 08:19.630
I would be completely broken if so.

08:23.860 --> 08:25.260
What are you laughing at?

08:26.160 --> 08:27.220
Mrs. Zhao is funny.

08:31.390 --> 08:33.299
Try this fish. See if it's good.

08:37.419 --> 08:38.150
How is it?

08:40.299 --> 08:42.760
This is the best fish
I've ever had in my life.

08:43.299 --> 08:44.430
Then have some more.

08:44.660 --> 08:45.660
How old are you now

08:46.230 --> 08:47.960
to be talking about a lifetime?

08:48.910 --> 08:50.420
Well then, can you cook as well?

08:50.420 --> 08:51.110
Yes, I can.

08:51.540 --> 08:53.460
Could yours be as good as Dad's?

08:55.230 --> 08:56.360
I can try it someday.

08:56.870 --> 08:58.330
He doesn't stand a chance.

09:00.780 --> 09:01.640
Thank you, Dad.

09:03.480 --> 09:04.290
This is nice.

09:05.270 --> 09:06.500
It's been so long since our family

09:06.500 --> 09:08.150
has gotten together like this

09:08.150 --> 09:09.820
to enjoy a good meal. Come on.

09:11.990 --> 09:14.320
Let's eat together more often from now on.

09:15.470 --> 09:16.530
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

09:16.740 --> 09:18.220
Before Mu arrived,

09:18.580 --> 09:20.700
we hardly ever saw Zhao around.

09:21.150 --> 09:22.150
But since Mu came,

09:22.460 --> 09:23.780
we've been seeing Zhao

09:23.990 --> 09:26.180
more and more often, haven't we?

09:26.350 --> 09:27.880
These two are inseparable.

09:28.350 --> 09:30.140
They've been like that
since they were little.

09:30.140 --> 09:32.070
That was when they were very young.

09:32.420 --> 09:34.080
These two are all grown up now.

09:34.230 --> 09:37.290
Things must be different from
when they were children.

09:38.420 --> 09:41.280
Sister Mu must really like
Brother Jin Zhao, right?

09:47.910 --> 09:49.970
Your sister is asking you a question.

09:50.180 --> 09:50.820
What?

09:51.350 --> 09:53.480
You like Brother Jin Zhao a lot, right?

09:57.270 --> 09:58.750
W-why are you asking that?

09:58.780 --> 10:01.030
Because you cried that one time
when you couldn't find

10:01.030 --> 10:02.030
Brother Jin Zhao.

10:02.920 --> 10:04.760
Really? When did that happen?

10:05.580 --> 10:06.270
Mu.

10:06.580 --> 10:07.500
How old are you now?

10:07.500 --> 10:08.830
Were you really crying?

10:11.070 --> 10:13.190
No, I was crying because...

10:15.420 --> 10:16.870
Because...

10:19.790 --> 10:21.320
Because I saw some letters.

10:26.240 --> 10:27.090
What letters?

10:28.580 --> 10:29.700
Some letters...

10:29.990 --> 10:32.520
which were hidden behind
the archery target.

10:58.910 --> 11:01.550
Brother, let's go to the beach tomorrow.

11:03.150 --> 11:03.750
Sure.

11:05.030 --> 11:05.700
Zhao.

11:06.350 --> 11:06.950
Zhao?

11:08.270 --> 11:09.200
Do you have time?

11:09.790 --> 11:10.340
Yes, I do.

11:10.860 --> 11:12.000
That's great!

11:12.180 --> 11:13.630
It's been so long since
we went out together.

11:13.630 --> 11:14.630
Great! Come on.

11:14.750 --> 11:16.210
Let's have another drink.

11:23.740 --> 11:25.070
What happened there?

11:27.510 --> 11:29.840
The floor is cold.
Let me pick it up for you.

11:36.750 --> 11:38.080
You did that on purpose.

11:38.260 --> 11:38.870
Yes,

11:39.280 --> 11:40.340
I did it on purpose.

12:02.460 --> 12:04.590
-This yacht is so big!
-How beautiful!

12:05.300 --> 12:06.700
The scenery is gorgeous!

12:07.230 --> 12:09.300
It's been so long since
we've been on a holiday.

12:09.300 --> 12:10.490
Today, let's all relax

12:10.490 --> 12:11.620
and have a good time!

12:11.780 --> 12:13.350
The sea...

12:13.630 --> 12:14.540
is so vast!

12:15.230 --> 12:16.100
How annoying.

12:16.630 --> 12:17.180
-I want a photo too.
-Today,

12:17.180 --> 12:18.780
let's all unwind and relax.

12:20.630 --> 12:22.290
Xin, come take photos with us.

12:34.350 --> 12:34.990
Today...

12:35.150 --> 12:36.400
-How is it?
-You have been working hard.

12:36.400 --> 12:37.940
We finally have a chance to relax today.

12:37.940 --> 12:40.030
If we are relaxing, why can't you
let me have a drink?

12:40.030 --> 12:40.890
Just wait a bit.

12:41.030 --> 12:41.940
If you want to drink,

12:41.940 --> 12:43.870
I'll drink with you tonight, okay?

12:44.510 --> 12:45.570
You little rascal.

12:46.350 --> 12:48.470
There must be a bar on this yacht, right?

12:48.470 --> 12:50.000
No, don't you dare tell him.

12:50.140 --> 12:52.540
I already said
I'll drink with you tonight.

12:52.910 --> 12:53.890
I'll tell you later.

12:53.890 --> 12:55.060
-Let's take a photo first.
-Dad!

12:55.060 --> 12:56.060
I want to eat fish.

12:56.580 --> 12:57.780
Dad will catch some for you.

12:57.780 --> 12:58.580
That's right!

12:59.060 --> 12:59.990
Let's go fishing.

12:59.990 --> 13:00.940
As long as you aren't drinking,

13:00.940 --> 13:02.500
-I want to go fishing too.
-we can do anything.

13:02.500 --> 13:03.700
-Let’s go.
-Let’s go.

13:07.350 --> 13:09.180
Why can't I catch even one fish?

13:10.740 --> 13:12.340
My fishing rod is broken too.

13:12.780 --> 13:14.240
I've got one! I've got one!

13:14.700 --> 13:15.750
Another fish!

13:15.780 --> 13:17.350
Here comes another one.

13:17.350 --> 13:18.990
That's amazing!

13:21.580 --> 13:22.580
Help me hold this.

13:23.060 --> 13:24.460
Be careful!

13:27.180 --> 13:28.910
Why haven't I caught a single fish?

13:28.910 --> 13:30.420
Honey, you could change careers.

13:30.420 --> 13:31.390
Don't be a chef,

13:31.660 --> 13:33.460
but become a fisherman instead.

13:33.720 --> 13:34.940
How's it going over there?

13:34.940 --> 13:35.820
Any signs?

13:35.820 --> 13:37.550
I can't even feel a single fish.

13:37.990 --> 13:38.700
Zhao.

13:39.510 --> 13:41.310
Auntie Zhao owes you an apology.

13:41.600 --> 13:43.510
You've been living away from us
for so long,

13:43.510 --> 13:46.170
and I haven't shown you
enough care and concern.

13:47.060 --> 13:48.330
Do you have a girlfriend?

13:48.330 --> 13:49.460
Tell me all about it.

13:52.180 --> 13:54.420
Our Zhao is so handsome.

13:54.620 --> 13:56.680
There must be many girls who like you.

14:00.040 --> 14:00.840
There aren't.

14:01.190 --> 14:03.350
What's Wan Shengbang's daughter name?

14:03.350 --> 14:04.480
Her name is Wan Qing,

14:04.990 --> 14:05.910
Snakey.

14:09.150 --> 14:11.110
Mu, why do you know so much?

14:11.660 --> 14:12.920
What's that girl like?

14:13.060 --> 14:13.780
She's great.

14:13.780 --> 14:14.640
She's very hot.

14:18.180 --> 14:19.580
What do you mean by "hot"?

14:19.610 --> 14:21.680
Her looks, personality, and figure

14:21.700 --> 14:22.540
are all pretty hot.

14:22.540 --> 14:23.510
Really?

14:23.700 --> 14:24.510
Zhao,

14:24.630 --> 14:26.540
do you like this kind of girl?

14:28.750 --> 14:29.460
No, I don't.

14:31.900 --> 14:32.630
How gossipy.

14:33.780 --> 14:36.270
Well, I am just trying to have a chat

14:36.460 --> 14:38.150
as the wait for fish seems pretty long.

14:38.150 --> 14:39.910
Yeah, we haven't caught anything in hours.

14:39.910 --> 14:41.040
Let's stop fishing.

14:41.840 --> 14:44.440
By the way,
there's a home theatre on the yacht,

14:44.820 --> 14:46.050
and a karaoke room too.

14:46.050 --> 14:46.990
Come on, let's stop fishing.

14:46.990 --> 14:47.820
Let's go sing.

14:49.030 --> 14:49.630
Zhao.

14:51.880 --> 14:52.690
I'm not going.

14:53.150 --> 14:54.350
I'm tired from driving earlier.

14:54.350 --> 14:55.470
I want to take a nap.

14:56.000 --> 14:57.110
I'm not going either.

14:57.110 --> 14:58.770
I want to look around the boat.

14:58.780 --> 14:59.710
I'll go with you.

15:01.140 --> 15:02.060
I just remembered

15:02.060 --> 15:03.660
I have a conference call with Nana

15:03.660 --> 15:06.460
to discuss the venue
for our next charity performance.

15:06.460 --> 15:07.150
Okay.

15:08.230 --> 15:08.870
Honey,

15:09.150 --> 15:10.950
let's go sing instead of fishing.

15:10.950 --> 15:11.990
Give me back my flask

15:11.990 --> 15:13.120
and I'll go with you.

15:14.020 --> 15:15.080
Keep fishing then.

15:15.590 --> 15:16.400
Come on, Xin.

15:16.420 --> 15:18.400
Shall we go sing together?

15:18.420 --> 15:18.990
Sure!

15:46.760 --> 15:48.160
Finished with your call?

15:48.630 --> 15:49.960
You're up from your nap.

15:51.960 --> 15:53.420
Do you want to go for a swim?

15:53.470 --> 15:55.670
Do you really like Wan Qing's body type?

15:59.140 --> 16:00.460
If you want to swim,

16:00.620 --> 16:01.540
I can join you.

16:03.630 --> 16:06.180
How do you know I can swim?

16:07.870 --> 16:09.060
If you can't swim,

16:09.420 --> 16:10.550
you can hold onto me.

16:11.970 --> 16:13.890
That's a pity.

16:14.150 --> 16:15.810
I'm actually a great swimmer.

16:19.350 --> 16:20.150
Then let's...

16:21.550 --> 16:22.610
do something else.

16:22.990 --> 16:24.390
No, no. The scenery here isn't nice.

16:24.390 --> 16:25.520
Let's go over there!

16:29.030 --> 16:29.760
Quick, hide!

16:31.180 --> 16:31.940
Come on!

16:33.360 --> 16:34.400
Good, right here.

16:34.420 --> 16:34.940
The view is nice here.

16:34.940 --> 16:36.780
Alright, let's take a photo.

16:36.780 --> 16:38.060
Perfect!

16:39.350 --> 16:39.780
Let's take a couple more over there.

16:39.780 --> 16:40.910
Let's go this way!

16:42.300 --> 16:43.300
This spot is good.

16:48.460 --> 16:49.520
What's that noise?

16:50.090 --> 16:51.750
Nothing, it's just a big fish.

16:53.700 --> 16:54.660
Mu!

16:55.060 --> 16:56.030
Sister?

16:56.350 --> 16:57.680
What are you doing here?

16:57.800 --> 16:59.580
Well, it was stuffy in the room

16:59.670 --> 17:01.530
so I came out to get some fresh air.

17:03.350 --> 17:04.280
All by yourself?

17:04.810 --> 17:06.940
Don't worry, I won't go into the water.

17:11.460 --> 17:12.920
Swim back quickly!

17:13.150 --> 17:13.910
Hurry up!

17:25.270 --> 17:26.400
Sister, here you go.

17:27.160 --> 17:28.420
One is enough.

17:28.630 --> 17:29.910
No, you need two.

17:45.380 --> 17:47.500
You scared me!
Why did you jump into the sea?

17:47.500 --> 17:49.360
Your nerves are just incredible.

17:51.310 --> 17:54.970
I didn't expect you could keep your cool
under pressure like that.

17:55.530 --> 17:56.290
Are you cold?

17:59.940 --> 18:01.740
This is ice cream Jin Xin gave me.

18:01.910 --> 18:02.800
She left two,

18:02.910 --> 18:04.310
which means one is for me.

18:04.660 --> 18:05.790
How do you know that?

18:06.310 --> 18:07.840
That kid knows everything.

18:08.240 --> 18:09.700
You're not even blood-related,

18:09.700 --> 18:11.270
yet you understand her so well.

18:11.270 --> 18:12.800
Are you two blood-related then?

18:12.800 --> 18:15.240
Am I the same as her, Brother Jin Zhao?

18:18.570 --> 18:20.170
You already know the answer.

18:57.110 --> 18:57.940
I'm dirty.

18:59.780 --> 19:01.170
I don't mind you dirty.

19:02.700 --> 19:03.350
Let me see

19:04.420 --> 19:05.390
where you are dirty.

19:05.390 --> 19:07.320
Brandy! This shampoo is really...

19:12.550 --> 19:13.260
Don't move.

19:13.820 --> 19:15.300
One, two, three!

19:16.140 --> 19:17.740
Jiang Mu, what are you doing?

19:17.980 --> 19:19.100
He has a strand of white hair

19:19.100 --> 19:20.870
and I was helping him pull it out.

19:20.870 --> 19:21.830
White hair?

19:23.790 --> 19:24.870
Oh my god!

19:25.150 --> 19:27.500
The former campus heartthrob
is aging prematurely.

19:27.500 --> 19:28.830
Where's the white hair?

19:29.000 --> 19:31.100
I threw it on the floor,
so you can't see it now.

19:31.100 --> 19:32.300
It's been pulled out?

19:35.220 --> 19:36.420
What brings you here?

19:37.750 --> 19:39.590
This shampoo works really well for Xishi.

19:39.590 --> 19:41.050
I brought it for you to try.

19:44.870 --> 19:45.900
Leave the stuff here.

19:45.900 --> 19:46.700
You can go now.

19:48.140 --> 19:48.620
Bye.

19:49.100 --> 19:49.660
Bye bye.

19:54.150 --> 19:54.940
He scared me.

19:54.940 --> 19:57.110
Brandy! Actually, I think...

19:57.420 --> 19:58.110
Scram.

20:00.310 --> 20:01.840
I really think it's not bad.

20:10.820 --> 20:12.410
Ji, are you done over there?

20:12.790 --> 20:13.650
Just a bit more.

20:19.590 --> 20:20.650
Wait for me inside.

20:32.550 --> 20:33.610
Let's take a break.

20:34.390 --> 20:35.700
It's fine, Master. I'm not tired.

20:35.700 --> 20:37.220
I'll finish fixing this car.

20:37.220 --> 20:38.420
Let's do it tomorrow.

20:38.830 --> 20:39.730
Go out and stretch your legs.

20:39.730 --> 20:41.550
It's okay. This is the last one.

20:42.030 --> 20:44.430
We'll be done once I help him
finish this up.

20:47.830 --> 20:48.590
Yang.

20:49.820 --> 20:51.680
Go out and buy me a bottle of water.

20:54.900 --> 20:56.050
I just bought water this morning.

20:56.050 --> 20:56.910
You can have it.

20:59.550 --> 21:00.730
It's brand new with the seal intact.

21:00.730 --> 21:01.790
Go ahead and drink it.

21:01.790 --> 21:03.390
It's really unopened. Look.

21:03.520 --> 21:04.850
I... I don't want water.

21:06.110 --> 21:07.710
Go buy me some coconut water.

21:08.340 --> 21:09.070
Make it cold.

21:09.150 --> 21:10.390
Didn't you used to
not drink coconut water?

21:10.390 --> 21:12.460
I suddenly have
a craving for coconut water.

21:12.460 --> 21:13.550
And it has to be cold?

21:13.550 --> 21:14.680
Yes, it must be cold.

21:17.320 --> 21:18.040
Ji.

21:18.830 --> 21:19.660
Go to the hardware store on West Street.

21:19.660 --> 21:21.220
Please buy some parts for me.

21:21.220 --> 21:22.510
I'll send you the model numbers later.

21:22.510 --> 21:23.070
But...

21:23.770 --> 21:26.050
Don't we have spares in the shop?

21:27.830 --> 21:28.690
I want new ones.

21:30.420 --> 21:31.700
Alright.

21:31.950 --> 21:32.970
Master, lend me your keys.

21:32.970 --> 21:33.830
I'll go by bike.

21:33.940 --> 21:35.240
Why do you need keys for?

21:35.240 --> 21:36.900
Let the bike rest. Go on foot.

21:36.980 --> 21:39.110
-Why does the bike need rest?
-Come on.

21:39.180 --> 21:39.790
Take this money.

21:39.790 --> 21:40.740
Get something to eat on the way.

21:40.740 --> 21:41.310
Make sure you eat enough.

21:41.310 --> 21:42.840
-Go on.
-Why are you so rich?

21:43.020 --> 21:43.390
Okay.

21:43.390 --> 21:44.270
Don't you want anything to eat?

21:44.270 --> 21:44.940
I'm not eating!

21:44.940 --> 21:45.550
Okay.

22:32.110 --> 22:33.110
Are they all gone?

22:34.020 --> 22:35.150
I sent them all away.

22:35.350 --> 22:36.180
Are you sure?

22:36.420 --> 22:37.180
Yes.

22:42.510 --> 22:43.310
Wait.

22:46.300 --> 22:47.410
Why is it here?

22:54.270 --> 22:56.200
Are you afraid it will tell others?

22:58.630 --> 23:00.560
Dogs are very smart these days.

23:11.150 --> 23:12.150
Are we good now?

23:39.340 --> 23:40.300
Focus.

23:44.330 --> 23:45.130
Are you sure?

24:14.020 --> 24:14.700
Nana said

24:14.940 --> 24:16.500
there's a meteor shower tonight.

24:16.500 --> 24:18.630
We definitely can't miss it this time.

24:25.500 --> 24:26.460
Then don't you

24:27.460 --> 24:28.990
fall asleep again tonight.

24:29.260 --> 24:30.860
If you do, I won't wake you up.

24:31.630 --> 24:32.550
Don't worry.

24:32.980 --> 24:35.150
Today, I drank your
special blend of coffee.

24:35.150 --> 24:36.950
I definitely won't fall asleep.

24:42.390 --> 24:44.070
But if I do fall asleep,

24:44.460 --> 24:46.320
you have to remember to wake me up.

24:48.140 --> 24:48.790
Got it.

25:13.300 --> 25:15.030
You brought strawberries too.

25:16.550 --> 25:17.410
They're fresh.

25:17.740 --> 25:18.310
Here.

25:40.320 --> 25:43.220
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

25:43.610 --> 25:46.580
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

25:46.830 --> 25:49.600
♪ Telling me ♪

25:50.890 --> 25:53.470
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

25:55.490 --> 25:58.720
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

25:59.230 --> 26:02.300
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

26:02.530 --> 26:06.380
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

26:06.760 --> 26:10.410
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

26:11.200 --> 26:13.720
♪ I watch you leave ♪

26:14.530 --> 26:17.970
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

26:18.430 --> 26:21.500
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

26:21.810 --> 26:24.970
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

26:26.560 --> 26:29.720
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

26:30.020 --> 26:32.960
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

26:33.440 --> 26:37.220
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

26:37.240 --> 26:41.930
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

26:41.960 --> 26:44.990
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

26:45.430 --> 26:48.880
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

26:49.030 --> 26:51.300
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

26:51.440 --> 26:54.580
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

26:55.310 --> 26:59.500
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

26:56.460 --> 26:58.190
The meteor shower is starting!

27:00.150 --> 27:01.210
Quick, make a wish.

27:04.020 --> 27:11.350
♪ I'll keep the light on for you ♪

27:08.640 --> 27:10.500
A-Are you not going to make a wish?

27:12.980 --> 27:15.650
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

27:16.160 --> 27:19.020
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

27:19.910 --> 27:23.600
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

27:22.700 --> 27:23.550
My wish

27:23.760 --> 27:27.350
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

27:28.070 --> 27:31.100
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

27:28.310 --> 27:29.570
has already come true.

27:31.610 --> 27:35.060
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

27:35.790 --> 27:38.060
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

27:38.420 --> 27:41.560
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

27:42.120 --> 27:46.310
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

27:44.630 --> 27:46.870
I hope that every day from now on

27:46.980 --> 27:48.350
will be just like today.

27:49.150 --> 27:51.310
I hope that we can be together forever,

27:50.830 --> 27:58.160
♪ I'll light it up, for you ♪

27:51.540 --> 27:53.200
and be happy every single day.

28:15.790 --> 28:17.070
Zhao, perfect timing.

28:17.500 --> 28:18.260
Quick, help me take

28:18.260 --> 28:19.660
an ID photo for the charity performance.

28:19.660 --> 28:21.190
It keeps going out of focus.

28:24.060 --> 28:24.690
Okay.

28:25.660 --> 28:26.390
Press here.

28:45.310 --> 28:46.020
Ready?

28:50.590 --> 28:51.390
Wait a second.

29:12.160 --> 29:13.420
Count three, two, one.

29:13.980 --> 29:14.700
Three.

29:16.050 --> 29:16.600
Two.

29:18.000 --> 29:18.560
One.

29:21.110 --> 29:22.110
Does it look good?

29:27.970 --> 29:28.580
Not bad.

29:32.420 --> 29:33.030
Don't go.

29:35.310 --> 29:37.440
We don't have a single photo together.

29:37.830 --> 29:39.700
Why don't we take this opportunity

29:39.700 --> 29:40.550
to set a timer?

30:30.580 --> 30:32.350
♪ Go, go, go, oh! ♪

30:33.110 --> 30:34.620
♪ What do you mean? ♪

30:34.640 --> 30:35.480
♪ Cherry blossoms ♪

30:35.510 --> 30:38.050
♪ At the moment
when cherry blossoms bloom ♪

30:38.070 --> 30:41.630
♪ The petals of love will also fall soon ♪

30:41.650 --> 30:44.380
♪ If you care about me just as you said ♪

30:44.400 --> 30:45.890
♪ Stop pretending and kiss me ♪

30:45.920 --> 30:48.030
♪ As if it's a homecoming ♪

30:48.050 --> 30:50.960
♪ Shake like an animation's protagonist ♪

30:50.990 --> 30:53.940
♪ We will shine if we have love ♪

30:53.960 --> 30:57.310
♪ Shake both hands like a clock ♪

30:57.330 --> 31:00.640
♪ Draw a cross and release your firework ♪

31:00.670 --> 31:03.870
♪ Come and see cherry blossoms with me ♪

31:03.890 --> 31:05.960
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:06.870 --> 31:10.100
♪ Come and see cherry blossoms with me ♪

31:10.310 --> 31:12.140
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:13.400 --> 31:15.400
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:16.620 --> 31:18.620
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:19.790 --> 31:21.790
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:22.980 --> 31:24.980
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:26.030 --> 31:28.350
♪ Come and dance with me ♪

31:35.660 --> 31:36.750
Good job!

31:40.180 --> 31:42.150
That was amazing!

31:42.350 --> 31:43.350
You danced so well.

31:43.350 --> 31:44.870
Thank you.

31:44.900 --> 31:46.450
Great work guys!

31:46.910 --> 31:47.660
Come, have some water.

31:47.660 --> 31:48.510
-Mu!
-Have some water.

31:48.510 --> 31:49.960
You danced so well!

31:49.980 --> 31:50.840
You truly are my

31:50.860 --> 31:51.940
center-position goddess.

31:51.940 --> 31:54.790
I was so worried.
Thank goodness nothing went wrong.

31:54.790 --> 31:55.990
Not just no mistakes,

31:56.150 --> 31:57.870
it was absolutely perfect.

31:59.450 --> 32:00.400
Why did you invite

32:00.400 --> 32:02.220
your classmates to cheer
while we were dancing?

32:02.220 --> 32:03.480
It was kind of awkward.

32:03.870 --> 32:06.020
This is your debut stage in Manshi.

32:06.220 --> 32:08.590
Everything has to be perfect.

32:09.070 --> 32:10.000
Thank you, Nana.

32:10.350 --> 32:11.210
Are you hungry?

32:11.310 --> 32:12.420
Let me take you out for a bite.

32:12.420 --> 32:12.830
Okay.

32:12.870 --> 32:13.400
Let's go.

32:13.590 --> 32:14.500
And forget about him?

32:14.500 --> 32:15.420
It's fine. He can wait.

32:15.420 --> 32:17.020
Where are you going, Mu?

32:17.180 --> 32:19.070
Mu, I'll take you to that place

32:19.180 --> 32:21.380
with the super delicious coconut cake.

32:22.550 --> 32:23.550
Is it very sweet?

32:23.740 --> 32:24.150
No.

32:24.220 --> 32:26.220
It's just very fragrant and crispy.

32:26.460 --> 32:27.460
-Hello.
-Hello.

32:27.490 --> 32:28.740
Two portions, please.

32:28.740 --> 32:29.940
Two portions. Got it.

32:30.700 --> 32:33.290
Please add more coconut flakes.

32:33.310 --> 32:34.900
There are so many delicious things here.

32:34.900 --> 32:37.560
There's so many.
I'll take you to try more later.

32:38.370 --> 32:39.090
Please add a bit more for me.

32:39.090 --> 32:39.790
Come on, bottom's up.

32:39.790 --> 32:40.990
Come on, bottom's up.

32:42.180 --> 32:43.390
Let's have fun!

32:47.020 --> 32:48.720
Yiwen booked a room at OPPS.

32:48.740 --> 32:50.020
Let's go there and have fun later.

32:50.020 --> 32:51.250
You should have told me earlier.

32:51.250 --> 32:52.770
I shouldn't be drinking so much tonight.

32:52.770 --> 32:53.980
Wouldn't that affect my performance?

32:53.980 --> 32:54.790
Why bother?

32:54.830 --> 32:55.380
Here.

32:56.660 --> 32:58.590
Being good-looking has its advantages.

32:58.590 --> 33:00.180
Don't you two have someone behind you too?

33:00.180 --> 33:01.650
You even have someone looking out for you
when you are out.

33:01.650 --> 33:03.720
W-We can't compare to you.

33:03.740 --> 33:05.600
Come on, let's hang out together.

33:06.040 --> 33:07.500
Drink up. What are you waiting for?

33:07.500 --> 33:08.390
Let's cheers.

33:14.660 --> 33:15.270
Nana.

33:15.460 --> 33:17.460
I don't feel well. I'll skip eating.

33:23.560 --> 33:24.150
Don't go.

33:24.910 --> 33:25.630
I'm sorry.

33:34.220 --> 33:35.020
What's wrong?

33:35.420 --> 33:36.620
Come, let's drink up.

33:40.690 --> 33:41.340
Coming.

33:53.070 --> 33:53.660
Here.

33:55.990 --> 33:57.190
What's going on?

33:57.300 --> 33:58.320
What happened?

34:25.120 --> 34:28.230
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

34:30.940 --> 34:34.130
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

34:34.920 --> 34:37.980
♪ About your news ♪

34:40.239 --> 34:43.889
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

34:46.210 --> 34:51.389
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

34:53.040 --> 34:56.639
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

34:56.949 --> 35:02.140
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

34:58.940 --> 35:00.200
I won't let you suffer.

35:03.630 --> 35:07.640
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

35:08.150 --> 35:10.010
A-Are you not going to make a wish?

35:10.520 --> 35:15.640
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

35:15.190 --> 35:16.020
My wish

35:16.040 --> 35:19.920
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

35:20.650 --> 35:26.690
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

35:20.830 --> 35:22.090
has already come true.

35:27.150 --> 35:30.790
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

35:30.710 --> 35:31.620
All my life,

35:31.280 --> 35:35.390
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

35:33.940 --> 35:35.710
people have come and gone.

35:35.720 --> 35:39.890
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

35:38.350 --> 35:39.910
I've never been serious about anyone.

35:39.910 --> 35:43.850
♪ To run towards you again ♪

35:42.540 --> 35:44.100
So once I get serious,

35:44.620 --> 35:48.570
Even if I have only you in my arms

35:46.940 --> 35:49.060
I probably won't give you
a chance to change your mind.

35:49.000 --> 35:53.210
♪ Meet the dusk with you ♪

35:53.370 --> 35:57.250
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

35:58.030 --> 36:04.070
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

36:04.940 --> 36:08.590
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

36:08.610 --> 36:12.720
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

36:13.100 --> 36:15.230
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

36:15.260 --> 36:17.070
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

36:17.100 --> 36:20.880
♪ To run towards you again ♪

36:21.250 --> 36:25.100
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

36:27.170 --> 36:30.640
♪ For a lifetime ♪

36:36.230 --> 36:38.960
Are you sure you don't want me to
keep you company?

36:39.750 --> 36:40.670
Just grab a car.

36:40.930 --> 36:41.800
Get some rest early.

36:41.800 --> 36:42.430
Okay.

36:53.830 --> 36:56.100
Yiwen, who you're looking for,
didn't come tonight.

36:56.100 --> 36:57.560
But he booked a hotel room.

36:57.870 --> 36:59.460
I'll send you the address later.

36:59.460 --> 37:00.590
Do you need any help?

37:02.310 --> 37:03.190
Not for now.

37:03.570 --> 37:04.220
Thank you.

37:05.830 --> 37:06.620
It seems that

37:06.910 --> 37:08.970
your life has changed a bit recently.

37:11.020 --> 37:12.480
Is our previous agreement

37:13.030 --> 37:13.840
still valid?

37:19.980 --> 37:21.110
What I promised you,

37:21.390 --> 37:22.920
I will definitely fulfill.

37:23.830 --> 37:24.790
But now...

37:25.390 --> 37:26.390
I need something.

37:26.670 --> 37:27.270
Tell me.

37:29.220 --> 37:30.420
The competition map.

38:24.350 --> 38:25.280
Where did you go?

38:27.350 --> 38:28.550
I just went for a walk.

38:29.150 --> 38:31.810
Did you have to turn your phone off
as you walked?

38:36.240 --> 38:38.240
Move aside. I need to get through.

38:41.020 --> 38:42.150
You've been crying.

38:42.730 --> 38:43.530
No, I haven't.

38:48.460 --> 38:49.500
I've upset you.

38:54.810 --> 38:55.360
Yes.

38:57.260 --> 38:58.490
You've upset me.

39:00.140 --> 39:02.140
What can I do to make you feel better?

39:15.100 --> 39:16.230
I can't feel better.

39:19.200 --> 39:20.860
I'll never feel better again.

39:27.810 --> 39:28.480
I'm sorry.

39:33.380 --> 39:34.060
I'm sorry.

39:35.420 --> 39:36.060
I'm sorry.

39:50.540 --> 39:51.230
Mu.

39:53.210 --> 39:54.540
It's not what you think.

40:25.100 --> 40:26.580
Z-Zhao?
